# ============================================================

# # double hash mid-line as text
= = double equals as text
+ + plus plus mid-line
- - dash dash with space (not a depth-2 bullet because of context?)

Edge: a line that starts "* " is important, but what about "*italic*"?
Markdown italic: *one star around word* should NOT trigger important.
Markdown bold: **bold text** should NOT trigger.
Markdown ___underline___ should NOT trigger underscore-label.


